<group name="port_pid_product_serial_number_vid_temperature_voltage">

</group>

textfsm_template:
Value PORT (\S+)
Value TYPE (\S+)
Value PRODUCT (\S+(\s+\S+)*)
Value SERIAL_NUMBER (\S+)
Value VID (\S+)
Value PID (\S+)
Value TEMPERATURE (\d+C)
Value VOLTAGE (\d+\.\d+V)

Start
  ^\s*Port\s+Type\s+Product\s+Serial\s+Number\s+Vid\s+Pid\s+Temperature\s+Voltage\s*$$
  ^\s*${PORT}\s+${TYPE}\s+${PRODUCT}\s+${SERIAL_NUMBER}\s+${VID}\s+${PID}\s+${TEMPERATURE}\s+${VOLTAGE}\s*$$ -> Record
